videos.headline: Jayhawks defense forces 1st turnover
videos.description: Kansas DE Dorance Armstrong Jr. forces Kansas State WR Byron Pringle fumble early in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Delton links up with Pringle for big gain
videos.description: Kansas State QB Alex Delton finds WR Byron Pringle over the middle for a 38-yard gain.

videos.headline: Kansas State defense attacking early
videos.description: On the first play of the third quarter, Kansas State LB Jayd Kirby forces Kansas QB Carter Stanley to fumble.

videos.headline: Barnes scores red zone TD
videos.description: Following the fumble, Kansas State RB Alex Barnes rushes up the middle for a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Sims hauls in great catch
videos.description: Kansas QB Carter Stanley connects with WR Steven Sims down the sideline for a 37-yard gain. After initially being called an incomplete pass, the call was overturned.

videos.headline: Sims breaks out for long gain
videos.description: Kansas QB Carter Stanley completes a 57-yard pass to WR Steven Sims late in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Martin's TD cuts into Kansas State lead
videos.description: Nearing 200 total game minutes without a touchdown, Kansas RB Taylor Martin bounces to the outside for a 5-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Barnes' 2nd TD extends Kansas State lead
videos.description: Setting up in the Wildcat formation, Kansas State RB Alex Barnes breaks out for a 9-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Stanley tosses 60-yard TD
videos.description: Kansas QB Carter Stanley finds WR Steven Sims Jr. for a long 60-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Booker hauls in jump ball
videos.description: Kansas QB Carter Stanley connects with WR Jeremiah Booker for a 39-yard gain late in the fourth quarter.
